{"tid":194246,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"報車禍新聞知道丈夫死咗 女主播強忍淚水完成工作","createTime":"2017-04-09T23:47:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-10T00:36:07.000Z","uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bacf429927c996ff2069f844e4bacd9c38fc0148","tid":194246,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T23:47:38.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">報車禍新聞知道丈夫死咗 女主播強忍淚水完成工作<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170409/56540289\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170409%2F56540289&d=D0cCki4bmudO7bhudq%2Byn04boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=a9f7cdad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170409%2F56540289&h=e4c5b6d3\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170409/56540289</a></span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n印度一名女主播在報道一宗車禍消息時，知悉其中一名死者是她的丈夫，但她仍保持記者的鎮定，直至新聞結束後才崩潰流淚。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170409/large/1491697602_6602.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170409%2Flarge%2F1491697602_6602.jpg&h=e6aecf66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n28歲的卡雅(Supreet Kaur)在印度電視台IBC24當主播，她日前在報道一宗車禍突發消息，從受訪者提供的失事汽車車款、事發地點和時間等資料中，已猜到是丈夫的車出事。然而她冷靜地報道這宗新聞和其他新聞，直至10分鐘新聞結束才哭起來。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170409/large/1491697526_4f0d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170409%2Flarge%2F1491697526_4f0d.jpg&h=a435ceec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一位編輯說在她報新聞期間，他們已知道車禍死者包括她的丈夫，但沒有勇氣告訴她。他表示她有第六感知道丈夫出事，但待完成工作後才致電給親友。她的一位同事稱讚她勇敢，新聞部雖感到哀傷，但亦以她為傲。<br />\n<br />\n卡雅與丈夫結婚只有一年，有一名年幼女兒。據說她丈夫的車被其他車從後猛撞，車內5人3死2重傷。"},{"pid":"9ead5388577850211aadbf529e6dc8830ded3498","tid":194246,"uid":44289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T23:51:50.000Z","msg":"敬業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />專業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64b628f354fbe0da178334bf2c5d8ab26a7b5575","tid":194246,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T23:52:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f940f0480e098c0522f924bf9598dae3c711c865","tid":194246,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T00:05:29.000Z","msg":"諗起呢套神劇<br />\n好多年前了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/lvp3H3cBBUA?t=14m37s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Flvp3H3cBBUA%3Ft%3D14m37s&d=D0cCki4bmudO7bhudq%2Byn04boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=b2bc7224\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/lvp3H3cBBUA?t=14m37s</a>"},{"pid":"d9f062a0544fce91b69568a235b387aa27de5993","tid":194246,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T00:33:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>諗起呢套神劇<br />\n好多年前了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/lvp3H3cBBUA?t=14m37s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Flvp3H3cBBUA%3Ft%3D14m37s&d=D0cCki4bmudO7bhudq%2Byn04boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=b2bc7224\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/lvp3H3cBBUA?t=14m37s</a></blockquote><br />\n日劇《新聞女郎》，韓國都有買版權翻拍過。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b79ef5f486d529c1d17e87e820ba75a57b4daad9","tid":194246,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T00:36:07.000Z","msg":"love is over~<br />\n現我再度孤獨～<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}